name: Crowned King
description:
From the sand quarries of Cameroon to the bright lights of Las Vegas. Son of Africa, Champion of the world. Francis Ngannou takes the throne.

There's something out there waiting for us, and it ain't no man. The Predator was once the scariest man on the planet, he is now the baddest man on the planet. Francis Ngannou is the first African-born heavyweight champion in UFC history.
